{"tid":2334961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本政府擬將核污水排入大海　IAEA準備派員監督","createTime":"2020-12-21T13:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T05:01:13.000Z","uid":159448,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"13064f4b30afd71cb5064fac1952af07fc377a40","tid":2334961,"uid":159448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T13:08:12.000Z","msg":"日媒12月20日報道，日本政府正考慮將用來冷卻福島第一核電站核反應堆、目前仍儲存在核電站內的核污水排入大海。國際原子能機構（IAEA）準備派員監督。<br />\n<br />\n《日本時報》20日報道，國際原子能機構（IAEA）總幹事格羅西（Rafael Grossi）受訪時表示，IAEA已準備好應要求派出監督團隊，以檢查經過處理的核污水、處理民眾對環境影響的關注。<br />\n<br />\n格羅西指：「如果日本政府決定好並邀請我們，我們可以在行動的整個範圍中合作，（包括行動的）事前（工作）、行動期間及事後（工作）。」他透露，IAEA正與日本政府就如何處理積累中的核污水舉行預備商討。<br />\n日本漁業人士強烈反對政府將核污水排入大海，他們擔心海產的聲譽受損。鄰近國家如中國及韓國也已就此事表達關注。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/564519/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E6%A0%B8%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7-iaea%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E6%B4%BE%E5%93%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%9D%A3?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_campaign=hk01&amp;itm_content=all&amp;itm_medium=web\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F564519%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25B5%25B7-iaea%25E6%25BA%2596%25E5%2582%2599%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%259D%25A3%3Fitm_source%3Duniversal_search%26itm_campaign%3Dhk01%26itm_content%3Dall%26itm_medium%3Dweb&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=1ba3d30d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/564519/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%93%AC%E5%B0%87%E6%A0%B8%E6%B1%A1%E6%B0%B4%E6%8E%92%E5%85%A5%E5%A4%A7%E6%B5%B7-iaea%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99%E6%B4%BE%E5%93%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%9D%A3?itm_source=universal_search&amp;itm_cam